        What is an HTML Table?
    </h1>
    <p>
        Tables in HTML consist of table rows <code>&lt;tr&gt;</code> 
        that have table data <code>&lt;td&gt;</code>. The table header tag <code>&lt;th&gt;</code>
        can be used instead of td to define a header. 
    </p>
</section>

